<HEADLINE> Zimbabwe Introduces Clocking-in System </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, March 27 (Xinhua) -- The Zimbabwe government has
introduced a clocking-in system for all civil servants ostensibly to
improve operational efficiency and accountability in the public
service, the country's national news agency ZIANA reported today.
</P>
<P>
