Islamic militants killed at least 11 people earlier this month in
Algiers and its suburbs.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, Algerian security forces have been launching an
intensive sweeping operation against Islamic militants over the
past several weeks, killing hundreds of them.
</P>
<P>
