<HEADLINE> Interviewees Refute Involvement in US Political Donations (6) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ma Zehua, entrusted by COSCO, made a formal statement that
COSCO is an enterprise group engaged in normal operations in the
world and never participates in any funding of the political
activities of any party, units or individuals. The so-called
COSCO's involvement in "political donations" is groundless
vilification.
</P>
<P>
"Therefore, we lodge a strong protest and reserve the right to
take any measures to protect the interests of the company against
any harms that have been done to the company," Ma said.
</P>
<P>
The three interviewees all mentioned that the 25-year history
since the resumption of trade between China and the United States
has shown that it is in the interests of the people of both
countries for the economic and trading circles of the two
countries to increase exchanges and cooperation and advance the
the bilateral relations under the principle of equality, mutual
benefit, and compensation of each other's needs.
</P>
<P>
Good bilateral relations will provide a sound environment of
cooperation for the enterprises of the two countries to promote
the economic and trade cooperation, they said. The essence of
China's so-called involvement in "political donations" is that a
handful of people attempt to place new obstacles and undermine the
development of the Sino-US relations by taking advantage of some
anti-China forces and news media in the United States.
</P>
<P>
They expressed the hope that all the people of insight will
resist the evil innuendos.
</P>
<P>
It is an irreversible historical trend for the improvement of
the Sino-US relations and further development of the economic and
trade relations between the two countries, and any attempt to harm
the fundamental interests of the people of the two countries will
never succeed, they said.  
</P>
