<HEADLINE> Chinese Premier Meets Bolivian President </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 28 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Premier Li Peng said here
today that China attaches great importance to its ties with all
Latin-American countries including Bolivia.
</P>
