leadership of the president in recent years to promote political
stability and economic prosperity, as well as to improve the
people's living standard.
</P>
<P>
China appreciates Bolivia's contributions to safeguarding world
peace and strengthening cooperation between the Latin American
countries, Li said.
</P>
