developing countries, and China would like to pursue economic and
technological cooperation with Bolivia on the basis of equality
and mutual benefit.
</P>
<P>
China adheres to the Five Principles of Peaceful Co-Existence
in handling foreign affairs, Li said, adding China's diplomatic
basis is to strengthen and develop unity and cooperation with
developing countries.
</P>
<P>
At the turn of the century, there are many problems that
international community should try to solve in order to safeguard
world peace and promote common development, he said. 
