<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, March 28 (Xinhua) -- Nigerian striker Kanu Nwankwo's
soccer career has not been definetely ended as the African
Footballer is making a rapid recovery, according to Italian club
Inter Milan on Friday.
</P>
<P>
Kanu, the sensation of last year's Atlanta Olympic Games,
received heart surgery and his playing future once seemed to come
into the end.
</P>
<P>
