May after several crucial clinical tests to be done to decide his
future.
</P>
<P>
Anyway, the team doctor said that Kanu's rehabilitation
progress "had stunned us".
</P>
<P>
Kanu, who underwent surgery last November after leading Nigeria
to Olympic glory, is following a sports rehabilitation programme
in the United States. 
