<HEADLINE> President Chirac Has Cordial Meeting with Qiao Shi </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, March 27 (Xinhua) -- French President Jacques Chirac
today had a cordial meeting with Qiao Shi, chairman of the
Standing Committee of the National People's Congress (NPC) of
China, in the Elysee presidential palace.
</P>
<P>
"I reaffirm here that France will further strengthen
Franco-Chinese cooperations in political, economic, cultural,
scientific and technological fields. For this purpose, I will
visit China in May," said Chirac.
</P>
<P>
